      "role": "user",
      "content": "I finally made it to the edge of the Grand Canyon. It's... it's everything I thought it would be. But everywhere I look, I just feel this heavy sense that I've seen enough. Like I've ticked all the boxes and there isn't really a reason to keep moving forward to the next stop. It just feels like I've reached the end of my itinerary.",
